      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Nominal Pipe Size refers to standardized pipe dimensions used in engineering specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Nominal Pipe Size refers to standardized pipe dimensions referenced in flange drilling templates.&lt;SEP&gt;Nominal Pipe Size is a classification system for pipe dimensions referenced in Table II-16.</data>
